  "3078500": {
    "name": "The Twelve Slot Saloon",
    "steam_appid": 3078500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/72f84b202fc4ebe5c000a9805b61037d.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/72f84b202fc4ebe5c000a9805b61037d.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/72f84b202fc4ebe5c000a9805b61037d.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Twelve Slot Saloon</i> is a<strong> </strong>quirky RPG about a cat who has the power to use their <strong>Save Data</strong> to travel through time and alter the world around them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can they somehow manage to find a <i>Happy Ending</i> in <i>The Land Without Happy Endings</i>?<br><br>This is a RPG created mostly by one person, <i>James Yevon</i>, with the exception of the OST which was created by <i>Hajile Cave</i>. <br><br><u>This game is a passion project that hopes to one day touch your heart and soul.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/108aaf3539e2a1142a22a2c7c12490d2.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/031610d80b1435ebba4a14a9d26f5d17.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/55b4c0adcda091fb54c4157ff6b7f281.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/55b4c0adcda091fb54c4157ff6b7f281.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/55b4c0adcda091fb54c4157ff6b7f281.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>While you're exploring the world of <i>The Twelve Slot Saloon</i>, you'll encounter enemies that will launch you into brilliantly crafted <strong>Turn-Based Battles</strong>, called <i>&quot;Silhouette Showdowns&quot;</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In these battles, enemies will attack you with a variety of <strong>Bullet Hell</strong> inspired patterns that will keep you on your feet. From jumping over attacks, to trying to platform mid battle, there's always something to watch out for!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/92de61f1218b96566325ad003856da2c.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/92de61f1218b96566325ad003856da2c.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/92de61f1218b96566325ad003856da2c.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>During your turn, you'll get a variety of options to choose from. If you want to resolve battles without having to fight, you can use <strong><u>ACTIONS</u></strong> in order to find a peaceful solution. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each enemy has their own set of <strong><u>ACTIONS</u></strong> you can choose from, each <strong><u>ACTIONS</u></strong> having a unique <strong>Mini-Game</strong> to accompany it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By successfully completing <strong><u>ACTIONS</u></strong>, you can fill up the enemy's <i>Pacify Meter</i>. Once the <i>Pacify Meter</i> is filled, you are given the option to end the battle without violence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/547870cca2ec06ff4e86497b64defe8c.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/547870cca2ec06ff4e86497b64defe8c.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/547870cca2ec06ff4e86497b64defe8c.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Opposite to <strong><u>ACTIONS</u></strong>, you are also given the option to <u><strong>ATTACK</strong></u>, for a more traditional RPG style of gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your turn to <u><strong>ATTACK</strong></u>, you'll be thrown into a <strong>Shooter Inspired Mini-Game</strong>. The goal in this <strong>Mini-Game</strong> is to deal damage to the enemy by shooting a target called a <i>CORE</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you deal enough damaged to the enemy, you'll be given two options. You can either Spare them, or Finish them off. Your choice here could greatly impact the story, so choose wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/456a9658148c97c3a25d48f7a544a69c.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/456a9658148c97c3a25d48f7a544a69c.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/456a9658148c97c3a25d48f7a544a69c.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Outside of <i>Silhouette Showdowns</i>, you can explore a beautiful desert <i>Wonderland</i>, filled with Charming, Quirky characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the path to your destination, you'll encounter obstacle courses that may prove to be quite a challenge, as you put your platforming and dodging skills to the test! You may also encounter puzzles that might reward you if solved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/282b17ba11a85e3ac5df882f347c7628.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/ca2e6ecff685d446418e01e6c97c4b07.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/ca2e6ecff685d446418e01e6c97c4b07.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/ca2e6ecff685d446418e01e6c97c4b07.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There once was a <i>Reaper of Death</i>, who one day, was charged to harvest a soul who was unlike any other they've ever encountered. This soul was kind, and selfless, and only wanted to bring joy to others. This soul never had any of their own dreams come true, but insisted on bringing to life the dreams of others... Until their own dying breath.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/c99e9f9a0d9f3f39052e10f954ef487f.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/c99e9f9a0d9f3f39052e10f954ef487f.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/c99e9f9a0d9f3f39052e10f954ef487f.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This one selfless soul inspired the <i>Reaper</i>, who wanted to carry on this legacy. So the <i>Reaper</i> created a world where dreams can come true, where anyone who receives an invitation, can make a wish, and live in this world filled with undying dreams. However, every wish does cost a price, that price being your soul. Despite that, a great many jump at the invitation, all in hopes to find a <i>Happy Ending</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/5976ac0343b146af86301851b1296ace.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/5976ac0343b146af86301851b1296ace.webm?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/5976ac0343b146af86301851b1296ace.mp4?t=1744651831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, someone new wakes up in the world; A cat who has no previous memory of anything at all, not even their own wish. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cat then encounters someone distantly familiar, and they realize this world where <i>&quot;dreams come true&quot;</i>, might be falling apart at the seams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/85e14594cdd322e1994ba6b0c159218c.webp?t=1744651831\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078500/extras/85e14594cdd322e1994ba6b0c159218c.poster.avif?t=1744651831\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=200 /></picture></span></p>",
